      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 119.3,
      "time_str": "01:59.300",
      "text": "狠了心 不必依靠人 最多",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 124.18,
      "time_str": "02:04.180",
      "text": "拥有不到风魔",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 129.11,
      "time_str": "02:09.110",
      "text": "很勇敢 道别坏心情",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 132.78,
      "time_str": "02:12.780",
      "text": "有好结果 不觉得几坎坷",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 137.8,
      "time_str": "02:17.800",
      "text": "愉快的节庆项目 自问能随心过",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 143.11,
      "time_str": "02:23.110",
      "text": "放过我吧不必找我可不可",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 148.06,
      "time_str": "02:28.060",
      "text": "难得轻松勿来难为我",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 152.4,
